  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37468</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、そう言えば、アルベルトって、ぼくたちと一緒に
食事してるけど、食べた物ってどうなってるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, by the way, Albert eats with us, but what happens to the food he eats?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38024</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>お、それ、オレも気になってた！
扉開けても、服しか出てこねーしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, I was wondering about that too! When you open the door, only clothes come out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クリュールゥ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Klyuruu...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ、おめぇらの薄っぺらい脳みそで考えたところで、
ぜぇーったいわかるわけがねぇーだーよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, no matter how much you think about it with your shallow brains, you’ll never figure it out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39824</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う〜ん……わたしたちよりいっぱい食べてるのに、
どこに行ってるのか不思議だよね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmm... He eats more than us, but it’s strange where it all goes...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;&lt;MEL&gt;が、おらに興味を持ってるなら、教えるだよ。
実は、おらの体の中というのは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If &lt;MEL&gt; is interested in me, I’ll tell you. Actually, inside my body...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41336</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いうのは……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Inside...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>体の中というのは…………実は…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Inside my body... actually...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………おらにもよくわからねぇだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I don’t really know either.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なにソレ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What’s that supposed to mean?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43960</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_024_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひとつだけ確かなのは、腹が減ったら、
何か食べたくなるってことだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The one thing I know for sure is, when I’m hungry, I want to eat something!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
